@page "/"

<PageTitle>SmartSpec 首頁</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">SmartSpec</h1>
    <p class="lead">智慧規格書管理系統</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p>請選擇您要執行的操作：</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center g-4">

        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm hover-effect">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                    <div class="display-1 text-info mb-3">🔍</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">搜尋規格書</h3>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">瀏覽所有文件或透過關鍵字搜尋特定規格。</p>
                    <a href="documents" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg w-100 mt-3">前往列表</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm hover-effect">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                    <div class="display-1 text-success mb-3">📤</div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">上傳新文件</h3>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted">新增 PDF 規格書或相關圖片到資料庫。</p>
                    <a href="upload" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-lg w-100 mt-3">立即上傳</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hover-effect:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        border-color: #0d6efd;
    }
</style>